---
import PageShell from '../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'quick-verdict', text: 'Quick Verdict', level: 2 },
  { id: 'comparison-table', text: 'Side-by-Side Comparison', level: 2 },
  { id: 'allianz-care', text: 'Allianz Care', level: 2 },
  { id: 'axa-global', text: 'AXA Global Healthcare', level: 2 },
  { id: 'bupa-global', text: 'Bupa Global', level: 2 },
  { id: 'pricing', text: 'Pricing Comparison', level: 2 },
  { id: 'best-for', text: 'Which Is Best For You?', level: 2 },
  { id: 'faqs', text: 'FAQs', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'Allianz Care Review', href: '/providers/allianz-care' },
  { title: 'AXA Global Review', href: '/providers/axa-global' },
  { title: 'Bupa Global Review', href: '/providers/bupa-global' },
  { title: 'Europe Insurance', href: '/best/europe-insurance' },
  { title: 'Allianz vs Bupa', href: '/compare/allianz-care-vs-bupa-global' },
];

const mainComparisonColumns = [
  { key: 'feature', header: 'Feature' },
  { key: 'allianz', header: 'Allianz Care' },
  { key: 'axa', header: 'AXA Global' },
  { key: 'bupa', header: 'Bupa Global' },
];

const mainComparisonRows = [
  { feature: 'Headquarters', allianz: 'Germany', axa: 'France', bupa: 'UK' },
  { feature: 'European Network', allianz: 'Excellent', axa: 'Excellent', bupa: 'Very Good' },
  { feature: 'EU Expertise', allianz: 'Strong', axa: 'Strong', bupa: 'Good' },
  { feature: 'Multilingual Support', allianz: 'Excellent', axa: 'Excellent', bupa: 'Good' },
  { feature: 'Mental Health', allianz: 'Enhanced', axa: 'Standard', bupa: 'Good' },
  { feature: 'Claims Speed', allianz: '10-15 days', axa: '7-14 days', bupa: '5-7 days' },
  { feature: 'No-Claims Discount', allianz: 'No', axa: 'No', bupa: 'Yes (up to 50%)' },
  { feature: 'Price Level', allianz: 'Value', axa: 'Mid-range', bupa: 'Premium' },
];

const pricingColumns = [
  { key: 'profile', header: 'Profile' },
  { key: 'allianz', header: 'Allianz Care' },
  { key: 'axa', header: 'AXA Global' },
  { key: 'bupa', header: 'Bupa Global' },
];

const pricingRows = [
  { profile: 'Single, Age 35', allianz: '€140-190/mo', axa: '€160-220/mo', bupa: '€190-260/mo' },
  { profile: 'Single, Age 50', allianz: '€240-320/mo', axa: '€280-360/mo', bupa: '€320-420/mo' },
  { profile: 'Couple, Age 40', allianz: '€280-380/mo', axa: '€320-420/mo', bupa: '€380-500/mo' },
  { profile: 'Family of 4', allianz: '€400-520/mo', axa: '€460-600/mo', bupa: '€520-680/mo' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="Allianz vs AXA vs Bupa: Best Expat Insurance for Europe 2026"
  description="Compare the top 3 insurers for expats in Europe: Allianz Care (Germany), AXA Global (France), and Bupa Global (UK). Coverage, pricing, and European network access compared."
  headline="Allianz vs AXA vs Bupa: Best Options for Europe"
  subheadline="Three European insurance giants compared. All have strong continental networks—here's how to choose."
  heroImage="/images/pages/provider-card-generic.png"
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Get Quotes"
  ctaButtonHref="/get-quotes"
>
  <h2 id="quick-verdict">Quick Verdict</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 my-6">
    <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-300 rounded-lg p-5">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-green-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Best Value</p>
      <p class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Allianz Care</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-3">German efficiency at competitive prices. Best mental health coverage. Strong DACH region network.</p>
      <a href="/go/allianz-care" class="inline-block w-full text-center bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white text-sm font-medium py-2 px-4 rounded transition-colors no-underline" style="color: white !important;">Get Allianz Quote</a>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-5">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-blue-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Best Balance</p>
      <p class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-2">AXA Global</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-3">French insurer with excellent EU coverage. Good mid-range option. Strong in Western Europe.</p>
      <a href="/go/axa-global" class="inline-block w-full text-center bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white text-sm font-medium py-2 px-4 rounded transition-colors no-underline" style="color: white !important;">Get AXA Quote</a>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-purple-50 border border-purple-200 rounded-lg p-5">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-purple-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Best Service</p>
      <p class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Bupa Global</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-3">Premium UK insurer with fastest claims. No-claims discount rewards healthy members.</p>
      <a href="/go/bupa-global" class="inline-block w-full text-center bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700 text-white text-sm font-medium py-2 px-4 rounded transition-colors no-underline" style="color: white !important;">Get Bupa Quote</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p>
    All three insurers have deep European roots and excellent continental coverage. Allianz offers the best value, AXA provides solid mid-range coverage, and Bupa delivers premium service at premium prices.
  </p>

  <h2 id="comparison-table">Side-by-Side Comparison</h2>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={mainComparisonColumns} rows={mainComparisonRows} />
  </div>

  <h2 id="allianz-care">Allianz Care</h2>

  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
    <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs font-medium rounded">German</span>
    <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs font-medium rounded">Best Value</span>
    <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs font-medium rounded">Mental Health</span>
  </div>

  <p>
    Allianz Care brings German precision to international health insurance. Backed by Allianz SE, one of the world's largest insurers, they offer comprehensive coverage at prices 10-20% below premium competitors. Their mental health benefits are the best of the three.
  </p>

  <p><strong>Strengths:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>10-20% cheaper than Bupa</li>
    <li>Enhanced mental health coverage</li>
    <li>Excellent DACH region network (Germany, Austria, Switzerland)</li>
    <li>Strong multilingual support</li>
    <li>Flexible, customizable plans</li>
    <li>German reliability and efficiency</li>
  </ul>

  <p><strong>Weaknesses:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Claims processing slower than Bupa (10-15 days)</li>
    <li>No no-claims discount</li>
    <li>Digital experience less polished</li>
    <li>UK network not as strong as Bupa</li>
  </ul>

  <p><strong>Best for:</strong> Budget-conscious expats in continental Europe. Those needing mental health support. Germans and German-speakers.</p>

  <div class="my-6">
    <a href="/go/allianz-care" class="inline-block bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white font-medium py-2.5 px-5 rounded-lg transition-colors no-underline mr-3" style="color: white !important;">Get Allianz Quote</a>
    <a href="/providers/allianz-care" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-medium">Read Full Review →</a>
  </div>

  <h2 id="axa-global">AXA Global Healthcare</h2>

  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
    <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-xs font-medium rounded">French</span>
    <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-xs font-medium rounded">Mid-Range</span>
    <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-xs font-medium rounded">Western Europe</span>
  </div>

  <p>
    AXA Global Healthcare is the international arm of French insurance giant AXA. They offer solid coverage at mid-range prices, with particular strength in France and Western Europe. A good choice for expats who want reliable coverage without paying premium prices.
  </p>

  <p><strong>Strengths:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Strong French and Western European network</li>
    <li>Mid-range pricing (between Allianz and Bupa)</li>
    <li>Good multilingual support</li>
    <li>Backed by major global insurer</li>
    <li>Reasonable claims processing (7-14 days)</li>
  </ul>

  <p><strong>Weaknesses:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Less distinctive than competitors</li>
    <li>Mental health coverage standard (not enhanced)</li>
    <li>UK presence weaker than Bupa</li>
    <li>No no-claims discount</li>
  </ul>

  <p><strong>Best for:</strong> Expats in France and Western Europe. Those wanting reliable coverage at moderate prices. French speakers.</p>

  <div class="my-6">
    <a href="/go/axa-global" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-medium py-2.5 px-5 rounded-lg transition-colors no-underline mr-3" style="color: white !important;">Get AXA Quote</a>
    <a href="/providers/axa-global" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-medium">Read Full Review →</a>
  </div>

  <h2 id="bupa-global">Bupa Global</h2>

  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
    <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 text-xs font-medium rounded">British</span>
    <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 text-xs font-medium rounded">Premium Service</span>
    <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 text-xs font-medium rounded">No-Claims Discount</span>
  </div>

  <p>
    Bupa Global is the premium choice, offering exceptional service quality and the fastest claims processing. Their unique no-claims discount can reduce premiums by up to 50% for healthy members who rarely claim—potentially making them cost-competitive over time.
  </p>

  <p><strong>Strengths:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Fastest claims processing (5-7 days)</li>
    <li>No-claims discount up to 50%</li>
    <li>Excellent UK network and service</li>
    <li>Premium customer experience</li>
    <li>Strong brand reputation</li>
    <li>Lifetime renewal guarantee</li>
  </ul>

  <p><strong>Weaknesses:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Highest starting premiums</li>
    <li>No-claims discount requires staying healthy</li>
    <li>Continental European network not as strong as Allianz</li>
    <li>Mental health coverage good but not enhanced</li>
  </ul>

  <p><strong>Best for:</strong> Healthy expats who rarely claim (maximize no-claims discount). British expats. Those who value premium service above all.</p>

  <div class="my-6">
    <a href="/go/bupa-global" class="inline-block bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700 text-white font-medium py-2.5 px-5 rounded-lg transition-colors no-underline mr-3" style="color: white !important;">Get Bupa Quote</a>
    <a href="/providers/bupa-global" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-medium">Read Full Review →</a>
  </div>

  <CTABox
    title="Compare All Three"
    description="Get personalized quotes from Allianz, AXA, and Bupa based on your specific needs."
    buttonText="Get Free Quotes"
    buttonHref="/get-quotes"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="pricing">Pricing Comparison</h2>

  <p>
    Prices shown in Euros for Europe-based coverage. Allianz is consistently the most affordable, AXA sits in the middle, and Bupa commands premium prices.
  </p>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={pricingColumns} rows={pricingRows} />
  </div>

  <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">
    *Estimated ranges for comprehensive plans with Europe coverage. Actual quotes vary by individual factors.
  </p>

  <h3>The Bupa No-Claims Factor</h3>

  <p>
    Bupa's no-claims discount changes the math over time. If you rarely claim, your premiums can drop by up to 50% after several claim-free years. This could make Bupa cheaper than Allianz in the long run—but only if you stay healthy.
  </p>

  <h2 id="best-for">Which Is Best For You?</h2>

  <div class="space-y-4 my-8">
    <div class="border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-5">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Choose Allianz Care if you...</h3>
      <ul class="text-neutral-600 space-y-1">
        <li>Want comprehensive coverage at competitive prices</li>
        <li>Live in Germany, Austria, or Switzerland</li>
        <li>Need strong mental health benefits</li>
        <li>Prefer German-style efficiency</li>
        <li>Don't expect to earn no-claims discounts</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-5">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Choose AXA Global if you...</h3>
      <ul class="text-neutral-600 space-y-1">
        <li>Live in France or Western Europe</li>
        <li>Want solid coverage at moderate prices</li>
        <li>Prefer a French insurer</li>
        <li>Don't need enhanced mental health coverage</li>
        <li>Value straightforward, reliable service</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-5">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Choose Bupa Global if you...</h3>
      <ul class="text-neutral-600 space-y-1">
        <li>Are generally healthy and rarely claim</li>
        <li>Live in or frequently visit the UK</li>
        <li>Value premium service and fast claims</li>
        <li>Plan to keep coverage for many years</li>
        <li>Can afford higher starting premiums</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="faqs">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

  <h3>Which is best for mental health coverage?</h3>
  <p>
    Allianz Care offers the most generous mental health benefits with enhanced coverage and higher session limits. AXA and Bupa provide standard mental health coverage, which may have more restrictions on ongoing treatment.
  </p>

  <h3>Do these plans cover EU-wide?</h3>
  <p>
    Yes, all three provide comprehensive coverage across the European Union and beyond. They all have strong networks in major European cities and understand EU healthcare regulations.
  </p>

  <h3>What about post-Brexit UK coverage?</h3>
  <p>
    All three cover the UK. Bupa has the strongest UK network given their British heritage. Allianz and AXA also cover the UK well but may have fewer direct billing arrangements with smaller UK facilities.
  </p>

  <h3>Which processes claims fastest?</h3>
  <p>
    Bupa Global is fastest at 5-7 days typically. AXA processes claims in 7-14 days. Allianz is slowest at 10-15 days, though still reasonable by industry standards.
  </p>

  <h3>Can I transfer between these insurers?</h3>
  <p>
    Yes, you can switch at renewal, but any conditions developed while on your previous policy become pre-existing for the new insurer. Consider this carefully before switching.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> This comparison is for informational purposes only. Prices and coverage details change. We are not insurance brokers. Verify current information directly with each provider before purchasing.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
